nodes.text: When Ahsoka Tano and Plo Koon visited Moshi Bar in search of information, Ahsoka used the Force to listen on people's conversations, one of which was this unidentified Quarren's. He owned a business, and due to the war, it was doing poorly. When a fight broke out between the Jedi and the patrons of the cantina, this Quarren did not aim a blaster at them, although another of his kind did.
